"4:61:7" : {s: 4, a: 61, w: 7, r: "نزل", t: "أَنزَلَ", l: "أَنزَلَ", lc: 183, tl: "anzala", lb: "অবতীর্ণ করা",e: "(has) revealed", b: "নাযিল করেছেন", i: "telah turunkan", f: 47, rm: "to descend, come down, go down, happen, alight at, settle in a place, lodge. anzala - to send down, give. nazulun - that which is prepared for a guests entertainment, abode, gift. manzil - mansion, station. nazzala - to cause to descend, send down. tanziil - sending down, divine revelation, orderly arrangement and authentic compilation, gradual revelation.", ag: "فعل ماض صيغة ٤", eg: "Verb Perfect 4th form", tag: "V", pos: "V", att: "PERF", qual: "(IV)", deg: "3", gen: "M", num: "S", mood: "", lu: "أَنزَلَ،أُنزِلَ،نَزَّلَ،تَنزِيلٌۭ،تَنزِيلُ،مُنَزَّلٌۭ،مُنزِلُونَ"},
